summary:
Over on my Instagram I just got asked if I could collaborate with anyone, dead or alive, who would it be? 
Of course I said...
body:
Over on my Instagram I just got asked if I could collaborate with anyone, dead or alive, who would it be?

Of course I said Taylor Swift, I probably wouldn’t have started playing music is it wasn’t for Taylor and her songwriting and musicality is so incredible. Also I love how generous, kind, caring and how much of an all around beautiful person Taylor is ❤️
